problem:
	I need to check my email and/or another site for an awaited message.

want to use as:
	cli - e.g. watch-site https://email.*.com, watch-site https://status.*.com

project:
	Watches site, on change of something -> notify

goals:
	cookies:
		use cookies
		figure out the UI for a cookie renew
	cli:
		maintain active watch sessions in local fs
		specify time between requests e.g. per 2 hours, per 3 hours....
	change:
		figure out how to define change in a site for a user.
	structure:
		split project into modules